data.description: Beautiful Casa Del Monte Condominium home has been upgraded with solid surface counters, laminate flooring, plumbing fixtures and many other fine touches. The open concept floor plan shows off the vaulted ceilings and corner wood burning fireplace. This home has a private fenced-in sunny deck with small garden area. It is Immaculate and in move-in condition; be ready to start enjoying the central coast beach lifestyle! There is a sand beach within walking distance. The furniture and furnishings are available separately.
